    public class Tinkerpop3CoreVocab_v10
extends com.bigdata.rdf.vocab.core.BigdataCoreVocabulary_v20151210
    Custom core Tinkerpop3 vocabulary. Applications should extend this vocabulary to include known constants that can be inlined into the vocabulary, avoiding the dictionary indices for higher performance. A good place to start for identifying these constants are known property keys in the application space.
